{"tid":2302562,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩睇動漫個時正大光明係老母面前倒左碗湯","createTime":"2020-11-27T08:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T05:17:37.000Z","uid":303864,"like":130,"dislike":97,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f6bf85f1e85ddc11a8b865af44ee4547f9f27f","tid":2302562,"uid":303864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:21:21.000Z","msg":"話說頭先我煲緊鬼滅動畫個陣<br />\n我老母無端端捧碗湯入黎叫我飲左佢<br />\n咁睇緊炭治郎屌打下弦之伍又點分神飲湯 咁咪話一陣飲<br />\n點知我老母5分鐘入黎煩我一次 最後我頂唔撚順係佢面前倒晒佢碗湯落地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住佢眼濕濕扮委屈咁拖返乾撻地 我心諗你一開始唔好咁煩咪得囉 你逼我飲我就係都唔飲呀你吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正皮:樓主做得啱 咁既老母係要懲罰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負皮:樓主冇做錯 咁既老母係要懲罰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62992fafa81e6a933a2a6ed42f862d5dce34a7ad","tid":2302562,"uid":303864,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:22:42.000Z","msg":"大家有冇啲類似既經歷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7b466a827e3a9029dda6691560db7f7aacb32b","tid":2302562,"uid":200529,"like":24,"dislike":6,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:23:23.000Z","msg":"負皮俾樓主的"},{"pid":"44b8290f91af9c226f5c0cbbb4ac3dab2e00083c","tid":2302562,"uid":370062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:24:14.000Z","msg":"本行認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367214e12fabac8cabd0b9636a3c3ff38f9ae912","tid":2302562,"uid":303864,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:24:50.000Z","msg":"有冇人老母都係咁煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b866994ed6a5ee7c9531136bb559e183cb6727c","tid":2302562,"uid":352074,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score"